sequenceDiagram
    box rgb(245, 247, 255) Customer
    actor Customer
    end
    box rgb(240, 255, 248) Sistem Web
    participant Web
    end
    box rgb(255, 245, 240) AI Engine
    participant AI
    end
    box rgb(255, 250, 235) Knowledge Base
    participant KB
    end

    Customer->>Web: 1. login(username, password)
    Web-->>Customer: 2. return: login berhasil
    Customer->>Web: 3. bukaHalamanKonsultasi()
    Web-->>Customer: 4. return: tampilkan form chat
    Customer->>Web: 5. kirimPertanyaan(prompt)
    Web->>KB: 6. cariKnowledge(prompt, produk)
    KB-->>Web: 7. return: context knowledge
    Web->>AI: 8. kirimKeAI(prompt, context)
    AI-->>Web: 9. return: jawaban AI
    Web-->>Customer: 10. return: tampilkan hasil konsultasi
    Customer->>Web: 11. lihatRiwayatKonsultasi()
    Web-->>Customer: 12. return: daftar riwayat

